com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models

Class ListContainersResult.Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.ListContainersResult.Container
  • Enclosing class:
    ListContainersResult

    public static class ListContainersResult.Container
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a container for blob storage returned by the server. A ListContainersResult.Container instance contains a copy of the container properties and metadata in the storage service as of the time the container list was requested.
